</div>
<div>
<p>　　高宗紹興初<pc>，</pc>惟用酒脯鹿ＭＺ<pc>，</pc>行<num value="1">一</num>獻禮<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="2" unit="years">
<num value="2">二</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>太常少卿程瑀言<pc>：</pc>
