</div>
<div>
<p>　　<date when="1006">
<date notBefore="1004" notAfter="1007">景德</date>
<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
</date>
<pc>，</pc>龍圖閣待制陳彭年言<pc>：</pc>
<pc>「</pc>
<quote>伏睹畫日<pc>，</pc>來年<measure quantity="1" unit="month">
